fields.name: CommunityName
fields.description: The name of the bgp community. e.g. Skype.

fields.name: CommunityPrefixes
fields.description: The prefixes that the bgp community contains.

fields.name: CommunityValue
fields.description: The value of the bgp community. For more information: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/expressroute/expressroute-routing.

fields.name: IsAuthorizedToUse
fields.description: Customer is authorized to use bgp community or not.

fields.name: ServiceGroup
fields.description: The service group of the bgp community contains.

fields.name: ServiceSupportedRegion
fields.description: The region which the service support. e.g. For O365, region is Global.
